page.title: 09A Day In My Life.
page.content: Normally I get up at 07.00, get dressed and let my labrador dog, Rocky, out for a walk.At 07.30 I have my breakfast_cereal,coffee and toast. At 08.30 my younger sister Lynne and I catch the High School bus at the end of our road and we arrive at Greenwards Primary School in time to start work at 09.00.Most days we do Kent Maths,Reading workshop or Environmental Studies.I like Kent Maths the best because every card is different.In the morning we have a 15 minute interval when we can eat our crisps.Later on we have 70 minutes for our dinner.After school ends at 15.30 my sister and I walk across the playground to the High School and wait for the bus home.
